xampp-tray (2.1.2) stable; urgency=medium

  * Refactored to modular Python package structure (src/xampp_tray/)
  * Added type annotations and pytest test suite
  * Replaced shell=True subprocess calls with explicit argument lists
  * Removed automatic XAMPP download from postinst
  * Fixed Architecture from all to amd64 (bundled Pillow native libs)

